This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to generate summary highlights at the sub-sentence level. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE) which are all relevant sub-categories.
